main event: On 26 Sep 1960, three unidentified flying objects were sighted over Italy.
interesting points: The objects were round, about 25 meters in diameter, and observed for 10 minutes., The sighting was corroborated by photographs taken during the observation., Similar sightings occurred in the same period., Witnesses reported the objects moving at high speed before disappearing., The objects emitted no noise during the observation.
witness description: local resident observing the objects in the sky
